data.description: A lot of potential here, 3 or 4 bedrooms all with closets.  Property sets on 5 acres with all of the possibilities you could imagine.  Property could also be used as Commercial.  The property has 2 storage buildings in back of home - one is 35ft x 20ft and the second one is 20ft x 12ft.  Electricity is provided in the buildings.    Some TLC and great location.
